{"type": "article", "id": 17595, "title": "Motus 灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-16T07:10:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110612ajPBGIlphvU5oLFm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏灯的名字是“Motus”，在拉丁语中是移动的意思。设计师的灵感来自随风摇动的草，胡桃木的灯头和下面的黄铜灯柱都是细长的，像植物的茎。可以随意调整倾斜幅度，旋转灯头，非常地灵活。这盏灯放在房间里并不显眼，但摇动时能打破原有房屋沉静的状态，带来一丝生动。<a href=\"http://www.morganruben.com/motus/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144712teDPBOfJFVkgv2WI.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"899\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144713fTYSq4VHRu8LdiDK.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"899\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144714KkjNpWCOAiMGdTqx.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1618\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144714Clbkh53zJ4wVX7AH.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"899\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}